<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11493] Autorestart option is not working because of stale znode  &quot;shutdown&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11493</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In hbase-daemon.sh autorestart option the znode used is &quot;shutdown&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
zshutdown=`$bin/hbase org.apache.hadoop.hbase.util.HBaseConfTool zookeeper.znode.state`
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; [ &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$zshutdown&quot;&lt;/span&gt; == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; ]; then zshutdown=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;shutdown&quot;&lt;/span&gt;; fi
        zFullShutdown=$zparent/$zshutdown
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the node shutdown is not available now and is changed to running.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Since this node is not available, script does not restart the node and it exists.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So autorestart scripts needs to be changed to  make use of &quot;running&quot; znode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
